## Stratum Usage

- **KV storage** ‚Äî growth signals, content performance records
- **Graph storage** ‚Äî content-to-keyword relationship graph (CSR on BRAM, 100K capacity)
- **Series** ‚Äî 365d retention for traffic and content metrics, 90d for growth signals
- **Streams** ‚Äî event streams with consumers for StreamSight, Cortex, analytics, alerting

