## Cortex AI Integration

- **Growth analyzer** ‚Äî `tide_growth_analyzer` runs daily scheduled inference on traffic metrics to detect patterns and growth signals
- **Content ranker** ‚Äî `tide_content_ranker` predicts search ranking and improvement suggestions from engagement metrics; retrains on drift
